.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH import 1  "import " 
.SH NAME
import \- Import secrets from a .env file
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmurk import\fR [\fB\-\-force\fR] [\fB\-\-group\fR] [\fB\-\-vault\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIFILE\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Import secrets from a .env file
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-force\fR
Overwrite existing secrets without prompting
.TP
\fB\-\-group\fR \fI<GROUP>\fR
Assign imported secrets to this group (default: everyone)
.TP
\fB\-\-vault\fR \fI<VAULT>\fR [default: .murk]
Vault filename
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIFILE\fR] [default: .env]
Path to the .env file to import
